NB. The reason-phrase depends on the return value.  If the return-value is OK (200-205), use 'OK';
NB. otherwise use y
if. >/ x >: 200 206 do. rp =. ' OK'
else. rp =. ' ' , ({.~ CRLF&(i.&1@:E.)) y
end.
h =. 'Content-Length: ' , (":#y) , CRLF
'HTTP/1.1 ' , (":x) , rp , CRLF , h , CRLF , y
