NB. See if header is complete
if. (CRLF,CRLF)&(+./@:E.) y do.
  NB. Strip header
  msghdr =. ( {.~ (CRLF,CRLF)&(#@[ + (i.&1@:E.)) ) y
  NB. Get rc line from header
